        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>文言虚词，极常考且易错</p>
<!-- more -->
<p><strong>考试频率:</strong><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><menclose mathbackground="orange"><mstyle mathcolor="red"><mtext>极常考</mtext></mstyle></menclose></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\colorbox{orange}{\color{red}{极常考}}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.2833299999999999em;vertical-align:-0.3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.9833299999999998em;"><span style="top:-2.98333em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.28333em;"></span><span class="stretchy colorbox" style="height:1.2833299999999999em;background-color:orange;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.28333em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.28333em;"></span><span class="mord boxpad"><span class="mord" style="color:red;"><span class="mord cjk_fallback" style="color:red;">极</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback" style="color:red;">常</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback" style="color:red;">考</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<ol>
<li>v. 到，去</li>
<li>第三人称代词
<blockquote>
<p>友人惭，下车引<strong>之</strong><br>
——《陈太丘与友期行》</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li>指示代词，这，此
<blockquote>
<p>皆是<strong>之</strong>类也<br>
——《郁离子·粤人食芝》</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li>⭐️助词，的，用于定语与中心语之间
<blockquote>
<p>然则天下<strong>之</strong>事<br>
——《河中石兽》</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li>⭐️位于<strong>主谓之间</strong>，取消句子独立性，<strong>取独</strong>
<blockquote>
<p>骨已尽矣，而两狼<strong>之</strong>并驱如故<br>
——《狼》</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li>协调音节，无义
<blockquote>
<p>久<strong>之</strong>，目似瞑，意暇甚<br>
——《狼》</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li>⭐️结构助词，疑问代词作宾句 或 否定句中，<strong>宾语前置</strong>标志，无义
<blockquote>
<p>孔子云：何陋<strong>之</strong>有？<br>
——《陋室铭》</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
